snippet.title: Kombat Kast 4 - Let's Discuss Invasions
snippet.description:
Join Tyler Lansdown, Derek Kirtzic, and Stephanie Brownback as they discuss Invasions in Mortal Kombat 1. Part of the fourth Kombat Kast, aired on 9/13/23.

Buy your copy now: https://www.mortalkombat.com 

It's In Our Blood. Discover a reborn Mortal Kombat Universe created by Fire God Liu Kang. Mortal Kombat 1 ushers in a new era of the iconic franchise with a new fighting system, game modes, and Fatalities!
